name: Unidentified_Sullustan_manager
content: A male Sullustan individual was the manager of Colliders Casino on the planet Lianna. Around 67 BBY, Darth Plagueis travelled to Lianna, hunting a Force-sensitive Shi'ido who had been using the the Force and his Skinshifting abilities to cheat at Colliders, the Casino's namesake game, as part of Plagueis' mission to eliminate potential rivals. The manager aided Plagueis in identifying his target.
